Executive Summary: Medical Specialization

QUENNE-MED represents a specialized implementation of the QUENNE architecture optimized for healthcare applications. It integrates quantum uncertainty quantification with neuromorphic continuous learning and medical domain expertise to create a clinically-validated AI assistant for healthcare professionals.

```
QUENNE-MED DOMAIN SPECIALIZATIONS
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  1. Clinical Decision Support System (CDSS)         │
│  2. Medical Imaging Analysis Suite                  │
│  3. Personalized Treatment Optimization             │
│  4. Real-time Patient Monitoring                    │
│  5. Medical Research Acceleration                   │
│  6. Telemedicine Enhancement                        │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

